<a href="http://www.indexmundi.com/commodities/?commodity=rice&amp;months=60" target="_self">http://www.indexmundi.com/commodities/?commodity=rice&amp;months=60</a></p><p>GINA, ‘Rice industry heading for new heights’, 28 August 2013</p><p>
